<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset='UTF-8' />
	<title>{{subject}}</title>
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
			line-height: 1.6;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			background-color: #f5f5f5;
		}

		.container {
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding: 20px;
			box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			background-color: #ffffff;
		}

		h1 {
			color: #0070c9;
			font-size: 30px;
			font-weight: bold;
			margin: 0 0 20px;
		}

		p {
			color: #333333;
			font-size: 16px;
			margin: 0 0 10px;
		}

		.text-center {
			text-align: center;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container">
		<h1 class="text-center">안녕하세요, {{name}}님!</h1>
		<p class="text-center">{{currentDate}}에 예약하신 편지가 도착했습니다.</p>
		<p></p>
		<p>{{textBody}}</p>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
